{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a941dc8973","title":"湖南部分地区发生春荒","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e661c57e64","index":0,"year":1957,"month":3,"day":18,"articleId":"a941dc8973"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"044b1148f1","name":"程坤"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fa0a8b6625","type":"title","text":"湖南部分地区发生春荒","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973"},{"id":"cd77c638e4","type":"authors","text":"程坤","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973"},{"id":"122e8fa445","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社长沙18日讯　湖南部分地区发生春荒。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973"},{"id":"9c537ed1f3","type":"paragraph","text":"洞口县目前无粮无钱的有三千五百八十六户，占总农户3．7％；有粮无钱的五千三百六十八户，占总农户5．7％，有钱无粮的二千九百五十三户，占总农户3．1％。全县粮钱发生困难的比上一周增加二千五百○七户。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973"},{"id":"ef375fc67f","type":"paragraph","text":"桂阳县九个重灾乡春夏荒缺粮农户占总农户20％。春荒问题大于夏荒，在缺粮缺钱的九千二百三十七户中有五千四百七十三户是春荒户。宜章县的十九个乡荒情面约占总农户10％左右。由于灾情继续发展，有些灾区劳力外流。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973"},{"id":"a78b5762f2","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：1957年3月18日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973"}],"page":{"id":"8151d7e6a4","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a941dc8973","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}